## 📋 Phase 3: Agent Skills集成 (Week 3)

### 目标
实现本地Agent Skills,让EVIF具备智能文件操作能力

### 参考资源

基于搜索结果,Agent Skills与MCP是两种互补的能力扩展范式:
- **MCP**: 标准化协议,连接外部工具
- **Agent Skills**: 本地能力封装,复杂逻辑实现

### 核心设计

```rust
// evif-skill/src/lib.rs

use serde::{Deserialize, Serialize};
use std::collections::HashMap;
use std::sync::Arc;

/// Agent Skill定义
#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize)]
pub struct AgentSkill {
    pub name: String,
    pub description: String,
    pub skill_type: SkillType,
    pub implementation: SkillImplementation,
}

#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize)]
pub enum SkillType {
    #[serde(rename = "file_operation")]
    FileOperation,
    #[serde(rename = "analysis")]
    Analysis,
    #[serde(rename = "automation")]
    Automation,
    #[serde(rename = "search")]
    Search,
}

#[derive(Debug, Clone, Serialize, Deserialize)]
pub enum SkillImplementation {
    #[serde(rename = "native")]
    Native { code: String },
    #[serde(rename = "plugin")]
    Plugin { plugin_name: String },
    #[serde(rename = "mcp_tool")]
    McpTool { tool_name: String },
}

/// Skill执行器
pub struct SkillExecutor {
    evif_client: Arc<EvifClient>,
    skills: HashMap<String, AgentSkill>,
}

